{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_16", "eventName": "反常光譜", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "16-9", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "瘋人的辯護", "storyInfo": "精神失常的礦工堅信他必須殺死這裡的村民，就像搶奪車輛時，他必須殺死自己的孩子。而在一場襲捲整個村莊的大火中，雷爾金以為自己的惡夢成真了。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "sn"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g14_ursusvillage", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烏薩斯的深秋，夜晚的氣溫驟降。寒風襲捲，吹得枝椏上的積雪紛紛飄落。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "空地上，人群早已散去，遠處錯落的矮屋也看不到一戶亮燈。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "空地中央的火堆裡，燒焦的木柴上依然殘存著一絲火焰，火苗被北風一遍遍撕扯，延續著最後的喘息。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firewood_throw", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_warmbonfire_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一根粗壯的木柴被丟進了火堆中，揚起的火星在空中飄散。"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們……", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道了我們的行蹤。", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "乾燥的木柴躺在焦炭中，漸漸被燻黑、變形，隨後被突然躥起的火焰完全吞沒。"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火光映照在虛弱的感染者的面龐上，他卻感受不到一絲溫暖。"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些人。這裡的……所有人。", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有把他們也抹去……就像抹去加尼亞……", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們才不必……", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#7$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必喪失道德，不必背棄純潔……", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#7$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必玷汙靈魂。", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#7$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他很痛，宛如鑽心之痛，像被針尖穿透。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他很冷，冷得無法停止顫抖，像掉入冰凍的湖泊。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他必須讓自己暖和起來。"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firewood_throw", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firewood_throw", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firewood_throw", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一根，兩根，三根。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一捆，兩捆，三捆。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原本微弱的火苗從木頭的縫隙中鑽出，變成一隻熾熱的魔鬼，它的火舌幾乎快碰觸到點火者的身體。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瘦弱的礦工拾起一根燃燒的木棍，朝著寂靜的房屋走去。"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_newiceforest_3", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噔，噠。噔，噠。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有節奏的腳步聲，一輕一重，一強一弱。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#4$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睡著……睡著！", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#4$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "全都睡著。", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#4$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們不知道自己會面臨怎樣的困境，會面對怎樣的審判。", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#4$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫助和包藏感染者，然後出賣他們。無知的人，溫馴如馱獸！", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#5$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，沒關係。", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會幫助你們，我能幫助你們。", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……因為我願意默想……", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#2$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並分擔……", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#2$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們的痛苦。", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#6$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "狂徒手握恐懼的火把，但零星的火焰已經不能抑制他的寒冷。"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他感到冰冷刺骨。寒氣來自礦石病，來自寒風，來自烏薩斯。"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他需要更多的溫暖。"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然間，一大堆乾草出現在他的視野中。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一場火。", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他拋下火把。"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一場淨化——", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#4$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火舌喚醒了所有枯萎。"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一次拯救！", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#5$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$firestorm", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_bat_act37d0d0_01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_062cg_phantom_front", "fade": "true", "fadetime": 1.5, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfire", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.7, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他從未如此清晰地感覺到，自己活著。"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g10_tent_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "腦內持續地嗡鳴，雷爾金努力想從惡夢中搶回一絲感知與理智。"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "五感正在一點點恢復，哀嚎聲卻仍未遠去，反而越來越近。"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他強撐著身體，步履蹣跚地朝帳篷外走去，想要呼吸一口新鮮的空氣。"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_smoke_01", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutry_3", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfire", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "灼熱的空氣撲面而來，身上的冷汗幾乎立刻被蒸發。"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一瞬間，所有的感覺全部回到了體內，刺激著雷爾金的身體。"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡不是夢境，這裡是現實。惡夢中的場景在現實中被延續。"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "四處都是逃竄的人群，那些曾為人們提供庇護的房屋，現在正被火焰摧枯拉朽地吞沒。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "升騰的濃煙裡，那些焦苦絕望的氣息如同魔爪死死扼住每個人的喉嚨，在這種威壓之下，人類渺小如蟻。"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1967_1#5$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷爾金！", "name": "尼克托"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1967_1#5$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡……發生了什麼事情？", "name": "雷爾金"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#6$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1967_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道，火是突然間冒出來的。這麼大的火勢我們根本沒辦法撲滅！", "name": "尼克托"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1967_1#5$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們現在能做的只有疏散大家！", "name": "尼克托"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1967_1#5$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷爾金，我們換來的糧食都還在裡面，我得進去——", "name": "激動的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡還有功夫管這種事！", "name": "雷爾金"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去把所有人叫醒！讓所有人都逃去村子外面！快，快走！", "name": "雷爾金"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而火場裡的人群並沒有因為雷爾金的話變得更有秩序，恐懼在肆無忌憚地蔓延。"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "bgeffect", "