": {"content": "不，這樣不對……我贏了，我殺死了他！", "name": "雷爾金"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能救所有人……！", "name": "雷爾金"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "r"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "r", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#6$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師！", "name": "別喬克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#6$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別喬克，你怎麼在這裡？快點去安全的地方！", "name": "雷爾金"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#6$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師，我、我……！", "name": "別喬克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽不懂我的話嗎？！", "name": "雷爾金"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷爾金想甩開別喬克的手，但小女孩用盡了全身力氣拉住了他的手臂。"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶，奶奶，她、她，不見了！", "name": "別喬克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼……？你不是一直跟她在一起嗎？", "name": "雷爾金"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#6$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "口吃的女孩雙手並用，試圖解釋發生了什麼，但她恐懼的表情已經說明了一切。"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尼克托！", "name": "雷爾金"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#5$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你繼續疏散大家，我跟別喬克去找娜迦夫人！", "name": "雷爾金"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#5$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1967_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好、好！", "name": "尼克托"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1967_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷爾金和別喬克穿梭在火場之中。兩側房屋燒燎，稍不注意，他們的衣服就會被火點燃。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶……嗚，嗚，奶奶！", "name": "別喬克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷爾金也想大聲呼喊，無力感卻在他的心中不斷堆疊，堵住了他的咽喉，讓他難以發聲、難以呼吸。"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他很清楚，如此猛烈的大火對一個行動困難的老者來說代表著什麼。"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老、老師，我……您……唔……唔！", "name": "別喬克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冒著黑煙的十字路口，別喬克摀住嘴指了指自己，又指了指雷爾金，最後指向了路的分岔處。"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不行……別喬克，你不能和我分開行動……你聽我說……", "name": "雷爾金"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#10$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師！", "name": "別喬克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女孩此刻漲紅著臉，豆大的淚珠從她的雙眸中湧出。她將雙手交握，做出一種奇異的、虔誠的祈禱模樣。"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不祈求皇帝，不祈求聖愚。她祈求雷爾金的幫助。"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "雷爾金"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#3$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id