 "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "霍里？你要去哪裡？！", "name": "雷爾金"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#6$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佝僂的背影並沒有理會雷爾金的呼喊，只是一步步朝著道路盡頭的火海走去。"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "四面八方的火光驅散了他的影子，猶如傳聞中走向刑場的聖愚一樣，像是要準備迎接火焰的沐浴。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-300,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "300,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別喬克，等等！", "name": "雷爾金"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至此，我犯下殺戮的罪過。", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不為食物，不為潔淨的水，不為溫暖的房屋。", "name": "霍里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他念誦著，步履不停，推開一扇燃燒的房門。"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "66_i23", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$firestorm", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfire", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.7, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷爾金的視線越過霍里，即便火光持續灼燒著他的雙眼，也無法阻止他看見房屋裡的一切——"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火焰猙獰翻騰，焦黑的梁柱搖搖晃晃，劈啪聲如垂死者斷斷續續的呻吟。"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而，一位老婦卻端坐在火焰間的方寸之地。"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "年邁的婦人"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她坐在僅剩的椅子上，木然無聲，火舌與她只有咫尺距離，卻彷彿被一道無形的牆隔絕開來。"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她周身纖塵不染，連頭髮也一絲不亂。她雙眼微閉，又彷彿看著一切。"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至此，我潔淨了他們的靈魂。", "name": "霍里"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}